        <item>
            <title>Google Translate 终支援广东话，更新后支援语言数量达 243 种</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/28/google-translate-5/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-translate-5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/28/google-translate-5/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[应用软件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Translate]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1246798</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p>Google Translate <span lang="ZH-TW">宣布，将透过</span> PaLM 2 <span lang="ZH-TW">模型的技术支</span><span lang="ZH-TW">援</span><span lang="ZH-TW">，新增</span> 110 <span lang="ZH-TW">种语言翻译服务，其中包括广东话。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">是</span><span lang="ZH-TW">次新增的语言支援，总共可以让</span> 6.14 <span lang="ZH-TW">亿人受惠，约占全球人口的</span> 8%<span lang="ZH-TW">。更新</span><span lang="ZH-TW">后，</span> Google Translate <span lang="ZH-TW">支援的语言数量接近翻倍，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">由</span><span lang="ZH-TW">原本的</span> 133 <span lang="ZH-TW">种语言增加至</span> 243 <span lang="ZH-TW">种语言。</span></p></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1246803 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240628at-1-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="575" height="329" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240628at-1-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/screenshot20240628at-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 575px" /></p><div><p style="text-align: center;">▲Google Translate <span lang="ZH-TW">宣布，新增 110 种语言翻译服务，其中包括广东话（图片来源：<a href="https://blog.google/products/translate/google-translate-new-languages-2024/">Google Blog</a>）</span></p></div><div><p>Google <span lang="ZH-TW">在</span> 2022 <span lang="ZH-TW">年</span> 5 <span lang="ZH-TW">月，采用了</span> Zero-Shot <span lang="ZH-TW">机器翻译技术，进行了一次大规模语言扩增。此后，</span>Google <span lang="ZH-TW">提出了「</span>1,000 <span lang="ZH-TW">语言计划」，希望借由</span> AI <span lang="ZH-TW">模型支援全球最广泛使用的</span> 1,000 <span lang="ZH-TW">种语言。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">而是</span><span lang="ZH-TW">次新增的</span> 110 <span lang="ZH-TW">种语言，约四分之一来自非洲，</span>Google <span lang="ZH-TW">或</span><span lang="ZH-TW">希望提升非洲地区语言支援</span><span lang="ZH-TW">为</span><span lang="ZH-TW">目标。更新还包含了来自吉布地、厄立特里亚和衣索比亚的</span> Afar <span lang="ZH-TW">语、几近绝灭的</span> Manx <span lang="ZH-TW">语、巴基斯坦的</span> Shahmukhi <span lang="ZH-TW">语、北非的</span> Amazigh <span lang="ZH-TW">语、巴布纽几内亚的</span> Tok Pisin<span lang="ZH-TW">等语言。</span></p></div><div></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">新增的语言清单包括广东话，但难以训练。由于广东话在书写上经常与普通话混淆，过去一直难以建立有效的翻译模型。</span>Google Translate <span lang="ZH-TW">资深软</span><span lang="ZH-TW">件</span><span lang="ZH-TW">工程师</span> Isaac Caswell <span lang="ZH-TW">表示，广东话是</span> Google Translate <span lang="ZH-TW">需求最高的语言之一。</span></p></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://blog.google/products/translate/google-translate-new-languages-2024/">Google Blog</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/chatgpt-edit-excel-google-spreadsheet/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】ChatGPT 连结 Google 试算表　可生成各式图表 + 计算数据</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/google-pixel-8a-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Google Pixel 8a　外形　手感　屏幕　相机　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/google-pixel-event-13-august/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Google Pixel 发布会 8 月举行，将展示新装置、新软件、AI 功能</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/28/google-translate-5/software/">Google Translate 终支援广东话，更新后支援语言数量达 243 种</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
